<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">فَأَقْدِمْ عَلَيَّ أَوْ لِيَ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[البحر الطويل]</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَإِنْ كُنْتُ مَأْكُولًا فَكُنْ خَيْرَ آكِلٍ ... وَإِلَّا فَأَدْرِكْنِي وَلَمَّا أُمَزَّقِ "<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> وَالشِّعْرُ لِلْمُمَزِّقِ الْفَيْدِيِّ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>